text:

In the middle of the night, I see you.
You came back for me.
You always end up coming back.
And I always end up taking you in.
I know, I have the right to destroy myself.
I do.
I am free to choose.

I felt safe

Sane

All this ridiculous chaos

text:

The skies rage as much as my heart.
1 month without you.
I'm still not at peace with it. I'm angry. I'm upset. 
But you see, amongst it all... flowers bloom. A sign of life.
Maybe one day I will bloom again.
